{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015jHYgNFiBoASaTe1DBRbND","type":"tool_result","content":"143\tdef buoyancy_draft(T_in, T_out, T_ref_cold, T_ch_top):\n144\t    \"\"\"Buoyant driving pressure [Pa] from the closed-loop momentum integral\n145\t    Delta_p = g * oint rho dz  =  g * integral_0^H (rho_cold - rho_hot(z)) dz.\n146\t    The descending cold leg (downcomer + inlet) is at T_ref_cold; the ascending\n147\t    hot leg follows:\n148\t      - z in [0, L_HEAT]: linear rise T_in -> T_out (heated risers)\n149\t      - z in [L_HEAT, H_DISCHARGE]: chimney, linear T_out -> T_ch_top (small loss)\n150\t    (Standard natural-draft relation, e.g. Bird, Stewart & Lightfoot \"Transport\n151\t     Phenomena\"; the cold-leg reference is the air entering the risers.)\n152\t    \"\"\"\n153\t    rho_ref = ap.rho(T_ref_cold)\n154\t    nseg = 400\n155\t    z = np.linspace(0, H_DISCHARGE, nseg)\n156\t    T = np.where(z <= L_HEAT,\n157\t                 T_in + (T_out - T_in) * (z / L_HEAT),\n158\t                 T_out + (T_ch_top - T_out) * (z - L_HEAT) / (H_DISCHARGE - L_HEAT))\n159\t    rho_int = ap.rho(T)\n160\t    integrand = rho_ref - rho_int\n161\t    dp = G * np.trapezoid(integrand, z)\n162\t    return dp"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e02d62b6-0fc3-47da-a384-485e72dab024","uuid":"38d99e28-7020-4c39-84cb-8692cd9fad53","timestamp":"2026-07-01T22:04:35.673Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/root/bench/cfd/output/rccs_model.py","content":"def buoyancy_draft(T_in, T_out, T_ref_cold, T_ch_top):\n    \"\"\"Buoyant driving pressure [Pa] from the closed-loop momentum integral\n    Delta_p = g * oint rho dz  =  g * integral_0^H (rho_cold - rho_hot(z)) dz.\n    The descending cold leg (downcomer + inlet) is at T_ref_cold; the ascending\n    hot leg follows:\n      - z in [0, L_HEAT]: linear rise T_in -> T_out (heated risers)\n      - z in [L_HEAT, H_DISCHARGE]: chimney, linear T_out -> T_ch_top (small loss)\n    (Standard natural-draft relation, e.g. Bird, Stewart & Lightfoot \"Transport\n     Phenomena\"; the cold-leg reference is the air entering the risers.)\n    \"\"\"\n    rho_ref = ap.rho(T_ref_cold)\n    nseg = 400\n    z = np.linspace(0, H_DISCHARGE, nseg)\n    T = np.where(z <= L_HEAT,\n                 T_in + (T_out - T_in) * (z / L_HEAT),\n                 T_out + (T_ch_top - T_out) * (z - L_HEAT) / (H_DISCHARGE - L_HEAT))\n    rho_int = ap.rho(T)\n    integrand = rho_ref - rho_int\n    dp = G * np.trapezoid(integrand, z)\n    return dp","numLines":20,"startLine":143,"totalLines":381}}}
